stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> LectureScheduled : Timetable Entry
    LectureScheduled --> AttendanceMarking : Teacher starts attendance
    AttendanceMarking --> NotificationQueued : Students marked present
    AttendanceMarking --> NoFeedback : All students absent
    NotificationQueued --> EmailSent : SMTP sends feedback links
    EmailSent --> FeedbackPending : Awaiting student response
    FeedbackPending --> FeedbackSubmitted : Student submits form
    FeedbackPending --> FeedbackExpired : Deadline passed (timeout)
    FeedbackSubmitted --> SentimentAnalyzed : TextBlob processes text
    SentimentAnalyzed --> SuggestionsGenerated : AI keyword analysis done
    SuggestionsGenerated --> StoredInDB : Record saved to SQLite
    StoredInDB --> DashboardUpdated : Teacher dashboard refreshed
    DashboardUpdated --> [*] : Cycle complete
    
    DashboardUpdated --> PerformanceCheck : Weekly automated check
    PerformanceCheck --> AlertSent : Score below 50% for 2 weeks
    PerformanceCheck --> NormalOperation : Score above threshold
    AlertSent --> [*] : Advisor notified
    NormalOperation --> [*] : No action needed
    NoFeedback --> [*] : No students present
    FeedbackExpired --> [*] : Link expired
